{
  "stem": "6159.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was a very frightening experience, for sure, because then we realized that we are all in danger and there was no way to get out of it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just were hoping that if we get to a ghetto, which they-- they-- they formed ghettos soon, and lots of people were sort of hiding.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're not hiding because everybody knew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were closing the streets where the Jews were, and that's what we called the ghettos.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we thought that it's going to be soon finish and then we won't be going out of the country.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But, one day came an order that every Jewish girl who is not married, or even if they're married, but they don't have little children, they have to get there in a certain point.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we-- I remember we were in the queue.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't take much with us, only what we had on, and we had to gather to go-- to go to a sports facility, which was open, only the-- the rows of seats, and we spend the night there.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we were distributed for different working camps.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had to walk two or three days to-- to wherever we should go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you think from the family?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was my-- on my own, but my very good friend from the building that I lived, she was with me all the way.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were together.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was younger than me, but she also follow that rule that she has to go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's how [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we both went and-- and started to dig trenches.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Budapest, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was two-- two different camps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One of them was [INAUDIBLE] and the other one was called [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
